和墨西哥，符合《美墨加贸易协定》的商品将继续获得豁免。 尽管特朗普声称加征关税将有助于为美国政府带来收入，并振兴美国制造业，但经济学家和商界人士警告说，这些关税措施将推高价格，损害美国消费者和美国企业利益，扰乱全球贸易，不利于全球经济发展。此前，已有多个美国贸易伙伴表示将采取反制措施予以回应。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"},"attached_info":"CkoIparMoeG+5ah0EAMaCTExNDMwNTcxNSC00ba/BjAAOOMjQAVyEzE4OTA5OTU1MzY1MTUwMTkyOTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"190 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1f854d4698bc70e25fe99e4c209dfeca_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1743698012.695647","card_id":"Q_1890009180531816320","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1890009180531816400,"title":"缅甸强震已致 4 名中国公民遇难，目前救援进展如何？当地华人生活情况如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1890009180531816320","type":"question","created":1743393303,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":76,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[36218,65008,97157,3136649,3917284],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"中国驻缅甸大使馆确认，截至北京时间3日16时，缅甸强震已致4名中国公民死亡，13名中国公民受伤。新华社分享页"},"attached_info":"CkkIparMoeG+5ah0EAMaCTExNDI1OTQ5OCCXpKi/BjAAOExABnITMTg5MDAwOTE4MDUzMTgxNjMyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"189 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-77e1116c491d64ddc413a1735ba15b3a_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1743698012.697129","card_id":"Q_1890777673967579540","target":{"id":1890777673967579600,"title":"中国石化与宁德时代达成协议，将共同建设一万座换电站，释放了什么信号？你怎么看「换电模式」的前景？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1890777673967579540","type":"question","created":1743576526,"answer_count":68,"follower_count":155,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url"