体结构。 近日，葛书菡收到了国家专利证书，这份专利不仅是对她创意的认可，更是为母亲在雨天撑起了一把温馨的“保护伞”。 解决雨天骑行难题？杭州高二女生拿下国家专利_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkoIparMoeG+5ah0EAMaCTExNDI5Nzc0NSCh6rO/BjAAOKYBQBRyEzE4OTA4MDI3MTc4MjEyMDc0MjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b6e6132aa0e7b77a921bc79bd206d93c_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1743698012.714798","card_id":"Q_1888685528414660511","target":{"id":1888685528414660600,"title":"黄金价格会不会迎来暴跌？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888685528414660511","type":"question","created":1743077720,"answer_count":223,"follower_count":632,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1346,26559],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2025年以来，金价的价格一路飙升上涨，再接下来会不会迎来一次大跌？"},"attached_info":"CkoIparMoeG+5ah0EAMaCTExNDIwMzc2MCDYgpW/BjAAOPgEQBVyEzE4ODg2ODU1Mjg0MTQ2NjA1MTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-30e1274542bb5540f711f7c47edf1995_1440w.webp"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1743698012.715418","card_id":"Q_23692643","target":{"id":23692643,"title":"雷阿伦当初为什么选择离开凯尔特人去热火？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/23692643","type":"question","created":1399530028,"answer_count":61,"follower_count":211,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,4196,35485,35502,36809],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"只是为了总冠军吗？可以从当初的选择可能性和他个人性格分析"},"attached_info":"Cj0IparMoeG+5ah0EAMaBzE2NTg2NTUgrMSsmwUwADjTAUAWcggyMzY5MjY0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"ht